\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4 , 
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **Resonanza**
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4  regolabili in tempo reale.\cb1 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ## 4. Prime Quantization
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 Quando \cf5 \strokec5 `Prime Quantization`\cf4 \strokec4  \'e8 attivo:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 1.\cf4 \strokec4  \cf5 \strokec5 `pigreco()`\cf4 \strokec4  calcola la frequenza teorica.\cb1 \
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 2.\cf4 \strokec4  \cf5 \strokec5 `quantizeToPrimes(freq, baseFreq)`\cf4 \strokec4  mappa il rapporto sul \cf5 \strokec5 `PRIME_GRID`\cf4 \strokec4  (2,3,5,7,11,13,17,19).\cb1 \
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 3.\cf4 \strokec4  La frequenza risultante viene clampata in \cf5 \strokec5 `[20, 440]`\cf4 \strokec4  Hz.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 Effetti sul suono:\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Introduce rapporti puri derivati da numeri primi.\cb1 \
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Riduce variazioni microtonali delle modalit\'e0, mantenendo armonici pi\'f9 stabili.\cb1 \
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Si combina con il profilo della modalit\'e0 attuale (es. tonalit\'e0 aurea quantizzata ai primi).\cb1 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ## 5. Interazione tra algoritmi e parametri
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 1.\cf4 \strokec4  
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **Scelta modalit\'e0 \uc0\u8594  \cf5 \strokec5 `setMathMode`\cf2 \strokec2 **
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4   \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Aggiorna pulsanti UI, pi.cfg, \cf5 \strokec5 `PiFX`\cf4 \strokec4 , \cf5 \strokec5 `PiReverb`\cf4 \strokec4 , scala LFO e filtri.  \cb1 \
\cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Richiama \cf5 \strokec5 `applyVoiceControls`\cf4 \strokec4  per riallineare parametri dipendenti.\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 2.\cf4 \strokec4  
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **Modulazione condivisa \uc0\u8594  \cf5 \strokec5 `updateAllModulations`\cf2 \strokec2 **
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4   \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Ogni ~50 ms aggiorna cutoff filtro per voce in base a \uc0\u960  depth, morph e profilo modalit\'e0.  \cb1 \
\cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  \cf5 \strokec5 `PiReverb.updateParameters`\cf4 \strokec4  riceve lo stesso timestamp (modulazioni sincronizzate).\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 3.\cf4 \strokec4  
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **FX non lineare**
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4   \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Slider FX \uc0\u8594  \cf5 \strokec5 `mapFxAmount`\cf4 \strokec4  (potenza 0.7) limitata a 0.65.  \cb1 \
\cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Ogni modalit\'e0 pu\'f2 biasare l\'92intensit\'e0 (es. TAU \uc0\u8594  bias >1 per ambienti pi\'f9 lunghi).\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 4.\cf4 \strokec4  
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **LFO Pitch**
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4   \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Ampiezza controllata da \uc0\u960  depth.  \cb1 \
\cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Velocit\'e0 e gain scalati per modalit\'e0 (es. ZETA3 pi\'f9 veloce, SQRT2 pi\'f9 morbido).\cb1 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf6 \cb3 \strokec6 5.\cf4 \strokec4  
\f0\b \cf2 \strokec2 **Morph**
\f1\b0 \cf4 \strokec4   \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  Varia panning e delay per crossfading spatial e tempo-correlato.  \cb1 \
\cb3    \cf6 \strokec6 -\cf4 \strokec4  In combinazione con TAU/ZETA produce movimenti ciclici.\cb1 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 ## 6. Flusso di segnale riassunto
\f1\b0 \cf4 \cb1 \strokec4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \cb3 ```\cb1 \
